&gt; For gnome users, see [i3-gnome](https://aur.archlinux.org/packages.php?K=i3-gnome&amp;SeB=x) in AUR
&gt; to add a i3 gnome session (gtk theme,
&gt; gnome-keyring, notifications, gnome
&gt; online accounts).

